snippet.title: Elon Musk SPEAKS On Rumors About Being Amber Heard's Baby's Father
snippet.description:
Elon Musk SPEAKS On Rumors About Being Amber Heard's Baby's Father

Join us in today’s video as we show you details about the rumors on Amber Heard’s baby father. Amber Heard last week shocked the world with a surprise baby announcement, one confirming the Aquaman actress has welcomed her first child. Posting for her 4 million Instagram followers, Amber introduced baby Oonagh Paige to the world. What’s more surprising is the baby is rumored to be Elon Musk’s.

Amber is currently in a relationship with Bianca Butti. Amber began dating Bianca in January 2020. Alongside her marriage to Johnny Depp, Amber has been linked to men including billionaire Tesla founder Elon Musk. But who really is the father? Be sure to watch the whole video because it’s pretty crazy! In addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
